Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算黑暗吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那持续闪烁的星屑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝阳那般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偶然遇到的纳玛的带路之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找冥王之壶的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子又和预想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上掉头的盔甲 海啸来临的疯鱼此类事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候才能找到冥王之壶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raider
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自黑暗的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底设了多少陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒霉的遭遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个大白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“做什么啊”个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你带路去寻找壶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可每次都是差点要挂掉的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说刚才真以为要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 即使我们有很多条命也不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可冥王之壶的线索现在只有纳玛知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许搞错顺序了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道冥王之壶所在的只有纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当时的纳玛失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知如此 我们还不顾一切地让纳玛来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来到这些乱七八糟的地方也理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要让纳玛取回记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我停下 不许逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷击破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起要取回记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是冲击疗法最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没听过这种说法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事都要尝试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷击破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不到黄河心不死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷击破之二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷击破之三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道会这样 才故意这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态不进展的话 我们就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地灵咆雷阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想起些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是撑不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得太过火了 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那种可怜的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽强的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些 小纳玛想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 有一只蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛在追一只蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就跟着蝴蝶的行踪找到了壶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 当真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是蝴蝶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此 可到底是哪里的哪只蝴蝶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边 那只在飞的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片花海中 盔甲少女追逐着蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的超现实主义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在变成盔甲之前也是个会追逐蝴蝶的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那可是很少见的蝴蝶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做黄凤蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄凤蝶 好像听过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛就是这样子追着蝴蝶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后来到一个很大的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样跟着蝴蝶 也未必能到达同样的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 蝴蝶有走同样路径的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就此追下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能达到壶之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在这种地方吗 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 蝴蝶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里 小纳玛曾经来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方居然有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这次找对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄凤蝶 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 能否见到真正的冥王之壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来里面很深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对的 对的 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这条通道有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的 小纳玛来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来证明给你看 请往这边一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此类陷阱到处都是 请小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事早点说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸盆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这里也充满了可疑的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方 真的有冥王之壶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说 谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不久之前有人来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是纳玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛知道这里的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很有可能就是我们的目标所在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下墓室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种遗迹一般都是权力者的墓室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里就是高官和家臣们的墓地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王之壶就被藏在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又在这种毛骨悚然的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 只能问雷藏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说雷藏为什么要做出冥王之壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏想将自己的灵魂转移到某些东西上以获得光明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是无法实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雷藏被封印的不是肉体 而是灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前神和魔王战斗时 魔王受到了神的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂被封印在人类中 不断转世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中之一就寄宿在红法师雷藏身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且雷藏也因此无法得到光明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才向别人出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏可是被称为“传说中的贤者”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向塔夫拉希亚伸出援手的也只有雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向塔夫拉希亚伸出援手的也只有雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所说得都是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我说的就有假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏为了医好双眼 反复进行各种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他 我的身体被融合了邪妖精及泥巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管出于何种目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能信任做出这种事的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏拯救了塔夫拉希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说那就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的善恶不是如此简单就能分清的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路 你也不是一度相信雷藏才跟他在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救人们的正义之心和封印着魔王的邪恶之心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个说不定都是雷藏的本性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人只有邪恶之心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像又不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来证明雷藏是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石棺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是沉睡着雷藏灵魂的壶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷藏的灵魂并没有沉睡在那个壶里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 杰洛士 为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 为什么那里没有雷藏的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是转移了那边那个盔甲灵魂的壶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说小纳玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雷藏灵魂沉睡之壶也是在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们魔族的目标不也是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些差异哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔族的企图是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事 调查这个正是我的使命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据事态的发展来看 对魔族而言可能也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 虽然稍许明白了些 但总觉得很心烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雷藏的壶到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 有什么东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意 这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能感觉到我的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了哦 祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来无论如何都要取我性命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是轻易就能治好的伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然敢出现在我们面前 说明他是有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁啊 莉娜的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙叫祖玛 是想取我性命的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你干的 绝不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的那位 被什么刺激得发狂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 纳玛 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰窟茑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无瘴界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔龙吠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤咒文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现吧 恐慌之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐慌之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃得下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方招出那种东西的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那位纳玛使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么纳玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是将转移到那个盔甲之上的灵魂放回本体而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么纳玛只是回到本体咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也要看本体现在在哪里 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在什么危及生命的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们所拥有的冥王之壶有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有冥王之壶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个里面沉睡着雷藏的灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为跟着莉娜就一定能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是花了不少时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷漠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你可是很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只对她有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比赞迪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然有人会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赞迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 比赞迪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我和纳玛在他的计算之外 所以撤退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是夸张的招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就用治疗咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说了 去比赞迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他手里有冥王之壶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然相信你 雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这家伙会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可不会轻易就死了
